{"tid":2026624,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［召喚寫信師］荔枝角在囚手足有事請大家幫忙","createTime":"2020-05-21T05:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T01:49:11.000Z","uid":69472,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"bba12eeeffe2507cb6e91a901d3bac909fb090d0","tid":2026624,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:32:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「沒有坐過監的人，不會睇到政府的真面目。」<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n在囚義士阿拔既家書，<br />\n向公眾揭露還押人士的苦況：<br />\n他們非但<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>投訴無門，<br />\n虐囚新聞更遭強權封鎖。</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n面對拷打與禁錮，<br />\n希望各位手足一人一信投訴柳記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n義士代我們承受牢獄之災，<br />\n我們亦再無理由，推卸改寫黑暗的責任。<br />\n<br />\n案例一、<br />\n<br />\n2020年1月<br />\n<br />\n有手足被職員打，<br />\n至今，手足<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">腹部仍留下明顯疤痕</span></span></strong></ins>，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可見該職員嚴重違反監獄規則；<br />\n<br />\n而手足亦即時向投訴調查組投訴，<br />\n而投訴編號：CSD CIU 1-70-A3-20(3)C，至今仍未有答覆。<br />\n<br />\n案例二、<br />\n<br />\n2020年2月<br />\n<br />\n有職員在活動室內叫所有黃絲站立，<br />\n其中一位在場手足不滿，<br />\n從而職員不禮貌對待該手足，<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">該職員（吳裕浩）蓄意作出刻意激怒在囚人仕的行為，嚴重違反監獄規則。</span></span></ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而該手足亦向投訴調查組投訴，<br />\n檔案編號：CID CIU-1-70-RA-20(41)C。<br />\n而該職員吳裕浩最近亦故意挑釁該手足。<br />\n<br />\n手足做唔到既野，<br />\n我地一人一信幫佢地做！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寫信template:</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XX1_nqfuSLdTaMymfs2g3nAxPbp_X5dX4PENNGhr0go/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1XX1_nqfuSLdTaMymfs2g3nAxPbp_X5dX4PENNGhr0go%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=c694eba9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XX1_nqfuSLdTaMymfs2g3nAxPbp_X5dX4PENNGhr0go/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">千祈唔好利用公司、學校資源print成疊出嚟比人簽名再寄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"963a9811919e942b8e9f33319d10762175ae5848","tid":2026624,"uid":69472,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RcX8ekG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcX8ekG.jpg&h=429c906a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足阿拔家書"},{"pid":"eb8ab1542542ccbf689df99043852500f34f8f42","tid":2026624,"uid":69472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:34:06.000Z","msg":"民記fb有家書全文：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103419337687469/posts/265182488177819/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103419337687469%2Fposts%2F265182488177819%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=8b2f2ba6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103419337687469/posts/265182488177819/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"8e81db7e73cc919099506fd5ce72abcc8c5ea6e5","tid":2026624,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:34:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal